WEBVTT

00:06.640 --> 00:08.576
announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:08.609 --> 00:12.413
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:12.446 --> 00:14.748
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:14.782 --> 00:16.717
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:16.750 --> 00:18.186
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:18.219 --> 00:20.321
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:20.354 --> 00:23.291
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:23.324 --> 00:25.693
- EVERYONE NODS AND SMILES
AND PROBABLY WILL SCREW

00:25.726 --> 00:28.762
THE ENTIRE DEAL BEFORE
MY FLIGHT LANDS AT JFK.

00:28.796 --> 00:30.331
YEAH, HANG ON.

00:30.364 --> 00:32.266
HOW ARE YOU DOING, LIEN?

00:32.300 --> 00:34.068
- GOOD MORNING...

00:34.102 --> 00:36.237
MR. HARTWELL.

00:36.270 --> 00:37.571
- [speaks Mandarin]

00:37.605 --> 00:39.807
- I HOPE YOU'VE ENJOYED
YOUR STAY IN HONG KONG.

00:39.840 --> 00:42.610
- TALK HIM OFF THE LEDGE.
IT'S ONLY 6 MILLION.

00:42.643 --> 00:43.811
ALL RIGHT, YEAH.

00:43.844 --> 00:45.213
YEAH, LOOK, I GOTTA JUMP.

00:45.246 --> 00:48.216
MY WIFE WANTS TO VIDEO CHAT
BEFORE I BOARD.

00:48.249 --> 00:51.119
[chuckles]
YEAH. NO, SHE'LL GO FOR THAT.

00:51.152 --> 00:53.421
YOU KNOW, WHY DON'T YOU
TRY ASKING HER?

00:53.454 --> 00:56.457
RIGHT. I'M HANGING UP.

01:04.832 --> 01:08.269
- HI, HONEY, HOW WAS HONG KONG?
- THE USUAL.

01:08.302 --> 01:10.304
YOU KNOW THEY, UH,
ALL SMILE AND NOD.

01:10.338 --> 01:11.239
THEY'LL PROBABLY SCREW UP
THE WHOLE DEAL

01:11.272 --> 01:12.606
BEFORE MY FLIGHT LANDS.

01:12.640 --> 01:14.275
WHAT'S GOING ON THERE?

01:14.308 --> 01:18.546
- NONSTOP SCHOOL STUFF,
THE HOUSE, OH, AND DON'T FORGET

01:18.579 --> 01:21.182
NEXT WEEKEND WE HAVE THAT
PRESCHOOL BENEFIT AT CIPRIANI'S.

01:21.215 --> 01:22.383
- YEAH, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.

01:22.416 --> 01:23.851
UH, MADISON IN BED YET?

01:23.884 --> 01:24.852
LET ME TALK TO HER.

01:24.885 --> 01:26.554
- SHE'S AT YOUR MOTHER'S.

01:26.587 --> 01:28.322
I WANTED TO CATCH UP
ON SOME SLEEP.

01:28.356 --> 01:30.224
- LET HER STAY.

01:30.258 --> 01:32.260
SURPRISE, I CANCELED LONDON.

01:32.293 --> 01:34.362
I AM COMING STRAIGHT HOME.
HAPPY VALENTINE'S DAY.

01:34.395 --> 01:35.663
- REALLY?!
- YEAH.

01:35.696 --> 01:38.266
- SO YOU'LL BE HERE TOMORROW?
- UH-HUH.

01:38.299 --> 01:40.634
- YOU KNOW, I DIDN'T
GET YOU ANYTHING.

01:40.668 --> 01:41.869
- WELL, YOU KNOW WHAT I LIKE.

01:41.902 --> 01:45.606
THAT, UM, SEE-THROUGH THING
WITH THE GARTERS THAT I GOT YOU.

01:45.639 --> 01:46.874
WHAT DO YOU HAVE ON NOW?

01:46.907 --> 01:50.811
- I TOOK A LITTLE CRUISE THROUGH
BARNEY'S LINGERIE DEPARTMENT.

01:50.844 --> 01:53.881
- WHY DON'T YOU...TAKE IT OFF?

01:53.914 --> 01:57.117
- OH, YOU MISSED ME.

01:58.719 --> 01:59.687
- THERE YOU GO.

01:59.720 --> 02:02.156
A LITTLE LOWER, LET ME SEE.

02:02.190 --> 02:04.192
[chuckles]

02:04.225 --> 02:08.262
[doorbell rings]
- HMM, NICE TIMING.

02:08.296 --> 02:10.264
CLEANERS.

02:10.298 --> 02:13.301
- [sighs]
COME BACK.

02:16.204 --> 02:18.572
- NO, STOP!
GET AWAY FROM ME!

02:18.606 --> 02:20.208
- SHUT UP!
- NO!

02:20.241 --> 02:21.309
- CHRISTINE?

02:21.342 --> 02:22.543
- NO!
- CHRISTINE, WHAT'S HAPPENING?!

02:22.576 --> 02:26.547
- NO, PLEASE, NO!
NO!

02:26.580 --> 02:27.881
- SHUT UP!
- AAH!

02:27.915 --> 02:29.417
- OH, MY GOD, SOME--SOMEBODY
PLEASE HELP!

02:29.450 --> 02:32.286
SOMEBODY CALL 911 IN NEW YORK!
- GET OVER HERE!

02:32.320 --> 02:33.487
BEND OVER!
- CHRISTINE!

02:33.521 --> 02:34.955
- [sobbing] NO!

02:34.988 --> 02:37.591
- OH, MY GOD.
CHRISTINE!

02:37.625 --> 02:38.959
- NO!

02:38.992 --> 02:42.162
- YOU CALL THE COPS,
SHE'S DEAD.

02:43.264 --> 02:44.732
- ALLEGED VICTIM
IS CHRISTINE HARTWELL.

02:44.765 --> 02:46.234
- ALLEGED?
- YEAH.

02:46.267 --> 02:47.235
THE HUSBAND, BOYD HARTWELL,

02:47.268 --> 02:49.737
SAYS HE SAW SOMEONE BREAK IN,
RAPE HIS WIFE.

02:49.770 --> 02:51.805
I MEAN, WITNESSED THE WHOLE
THING ON vCHAT.

02:51.839 --> 02:53.974
- OKAY, WHERE WAS HE?
- HONG KONG INTERNATIONAL.

02:54.007 --> 02:56.477
- HE CALLED HIS MOTHER, TOLD HER
NOT TO CALL THE POLICE.

02:56.510 --> 02:58.746
SHE COULDN'T SLEEP,
CALLS AN HOUR AGO.

02:58.779 --> 03:01.349
UNIs GET HERE,
THERE'S NO CHRISTINE.

03:02.950 --> 03:05.653
- NO SIGN OF FORCED ENTRY.

03:05.686 --> 03:08.289
BOTH DOORS LOOK UNTOUCHED.
SOMEONE SHE KNEW?

03:08.322 --> 03:09.957
- WELL, MAYBE NOT.
VIDEO CAM'S OUT.

03:09.990 --> 03:11.292
SHE OPENS THE DOOR,

03:11.325 --> 03:13.494
HE PUSHES IN,
SIGN OF A STRUGGLE.

03:13.527 --> 03:14.862
- THEY HAVE A DAUGHTER.

03:14.895 --> 03:16.664
WHERE IS SHE?
- MADISON, FIVE.

03:16.697 --> 03:19.633
GRANDMOTHER SAID SHE STAYED
WITH HER LAST NIGHT.

03:19.667 --> 03:20.834
- OKAY.

03:20.868 --> 03:23.304
GET CSU IN HERE.

03:23.337 --> 03:25.506
AND TARU, SEE IF THEY
CAN RETRIEVE

03:25.539 --> 03:27.241
AN IMAGE OFF THIS LAPTOP.

03:27.275 --> 03:29.310
- WE GOT SOME BLOOD.

03:29.343 --> 03:31.812
- SO HE RAPES HER
HERE ON THE COUNTER

03:31.845 --> 03:33.381
IN FULL VIEW OF THE SCREEN.

03:33.414 --> 03:35.015
- YEAH, SHOWS THE HUSBAND
HE MEANS BUSINESS.

03:35.048 --> 03:37.751
IT'S DELIBERATE,
COULD BE PERSONAL.

03:37.785 --> 03:39.487
- AND HE FORCES HER
TO LEAVE WITH HIM?

03:39.520 --> 03:42.022
- THE NEIGHBORS DIDN'T SEE
OR HEAR A THING.

03:42.055 --> 03:45.593
- NO ONE COMING IN OR OUT OF
THIS HOUSE LAST NIGHT.

03:45.626 --> 03:47.761
- THIS DOOR'S OPEN.

03:47.795 --> 03:49.263
THEY LEFT OUT THE BACK.

03:49.297 --> 03:51.365
- HUSBAND SAY ANYTHING
ABOUT A RANSOM DEMAND?

03:51.399 --> 03:52.566
- NOTHING WE'VE HEARD.

03:52.600 --> 03:53.834
NO ONE'S BEEN ABLE
TO REACH HIM.

03:53.867 --> 03:56.970
HIS PLANE LANDS AT NOON.
- 16 HOURS.

03:57.004 --> 04:00.274
GOTTA BE THE LONGEST
FLIGHT OF HIS LIFE.

04:50.491 --> 04:51.759
- WHEN'S MOMMY COMING HOME?

04:51.792 --> 04:53.994
- SOON, SWEETHEART.
ISN'T THAT BELLA?

04:54.027 --> 04:57.931
GO--GO PLAY PRINCESS WITH HER.

04:57.965 --> 05:01.835
MY SON TOLD ME THE INTRUDER
SAID IF I CALLED THE POLICE,

05:01.869 --> 05:04.338
THEY'D KILL CHRISTINE.

05:04.372 --> 05:05.839
I HOPE I'VE DONE
THE RIGHT THING.

05:05.873 --> 05:07.441
- YOU DID, MA'AM.

05:07.475 --> 05:09.042
NOW WHEN'S THE LAST TIME YOU SAW
YOUR DAUGHTER-IN-LAW?

05:09.076 --> 05:11.011
- YESTERDAY.
YESTERDAY AFTERNOON.

05:11.044 --> 05:12.813
SHE DROPPED OFF MADISON.

05:12.846 --> 05:15.516
- DID SHE SEEM UPSET OR ANXIOUS?
- NO.

05:15.549 --> 05:19.487
CHRISTINE IS ALWAYS SO BRIGHT,
SO FULL OF LIFE.

05:19.520 --> 05:20.721
EVERYBODY ADORES HER.

05:20.754 --> 05:22.823
- NOW WHAT ABOUT BOYD?

05:22.856 --> 05:24.425
BEEN ANY PROBLEMS?

05:24.458 --> 05:25.826
- BOYD WORKS A LOT.

05:25.859 --> 05:28.429
BUT HIS FAMILY ALWAYS
COMES FIRST.

05:28.462 --> 05:34.034
AFTER TEN YEARS OF MARRIAGE,
THOSE TWO ARE STILL SO IN LOVE.

05:34.067 --> 05:35.202
- ALL WE KNOW FOR SURE IS THAT
CHRISTINE'S BEEN MISSING

05:35.235 --> 05:38.606
FOR 12 HOURS, AND OUR ONLY
WITNESS IS STILL IN THE AIR.

05:38.639 --> 05:40.007
- NO ACTIVITY
ON HER CREDIT CARDS,

05:40.040 --> 05:41.675
HER CELL'S OFF,
TARU'S CHECKING IT.

05:41.709 --> 05:43.777
- ALL RIGHT,
IF THIS IS A RAPE-ABDUCTION,

05:43.811 --> 05:46.146
ODDS ARE IT'S SOMEBODY
SHE'S CROSSED PATHS WITH.

05:46.179 --> 05:48.048
WHAT DO WE KNOW
ABOUT THIS COUPLE?

05:48.081 --> 05:50.518
- WELL, THEY'RE LIVING
THE UPPER EAST SIDE DREAM.

05:50.551 --> 05:53.921
I MEAN, BOYD AND HIS PARTNER
JUSTIN GELD,

05:53.954 --> 05:56.123
THEY LEFT MORGAN, STARTED UP
NEW MARKETS HEDGE FUND

05:56.156 --> 05:57.525
A COUPLE YEARS AGO.

05:57.558 --> 05:58.526
CHRISTINE'S
A STAY-AT-HOME MOM.

05:58.559 --> 05:59.527
SHE'S ON THE PARENT'S BOARD

05:59.560 --> 06:00.461
OF HER DAUGHTER'S PRESCHOOL.

06:00.494 --> 06:02.663
- THEY DO THE REGULAR
RICH PEOPLE MAMBO.

06:02.696 --> 06:04.998
WINTERS IN VAIL,
SUMMERS IN THE HAMPTONS.

06:05.032 --> 06:08.469
- HIS HEDGE FUND--THIS ECONOMY
CAN BE A HIGH-WIRE ACT.

06:08.502 --> 06:09.403
ANY ANGRY INVESTORS?

06:09.437 --> 06:11.171
- YEAH, THERE WERE
A COUPLE OF COMPLAINTS

06:11.204 --> 06:12.673
FILED AGAINST BOYD'S PARTNER.

06:12.706 --> 06:14.642
SO THE COMPANY
AND BOYD PAID SOME FINES,

06:14.675 --> 06:17.010
ADMITTED NO WRONGDOING--
THE COMPLAINTS WERE WITHDRAWN.

06:17.044 --> 06:18.812
- WELL, THAT'S GOTTA BE HARD
ON A PARTNERSHIP,

06:18.846 --> 06:20.013
AND THIS MIGHT BE TOO.

06:20.047 --> 06:21.649
NOW, ACCORDING TO
CHRISTINE'S CALENDAR,

06:21.682 --> 06:23.817
SHE HAD LUNCH
WITH GELD ON FRIDAY.

06:23.851 --> 06:27.821
A MONTH AGO, HER HUSBAND'S
IN BRAZIL--ANOTHER LUNCH.

06:27.855 --> 06:29.523
- OKAY, FIN, ROLLINS, FIND OUT

06:29.557 --> 06:31.525
WHAT'S UP WITH THE LADY
AND HER LUNCHES.

06:31.559 --> 06:34.061
YOU TWO, MEET THE HUSBAND'S
PLANE AT JFK.

06:34.094 --> 06:35.729
HE DIDN'T WANT NYPD CALLED.

06:35.763 --> 06:38.766
LET'S NOT GIVE HIM
A CHANCE TO GO ROGUE.

06:40.501 --> 06:42.169
- WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
I HEARD FROM CHRISTINE?

06:42.202 --> 06:43.804
MY WIFE SAW HER
AT THE PLANNING MEETING

06:43.837 --> 06:45.105
FOR THE PRESCHOOL BENEFIT.

06:45.138 --> 06:46.474
- WAS THAT BEFORE OR AFTER YOU

06:46.507 --> 06:50.010
AND CHRISTINE
HAD LUNCH ON FRIDAY?

06:50.043 --> 06:52.613
- I DON'T KNOW ABOUT THE S.E.C.,
BUT IT AIN'T A GOOD IDEA

06:52.646 --> 06:55.516
TO LIE TO NYPD.

06:55.549 --> 06:57.217
- WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

06:57.250 --> 06:59.520
- WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW CHRISTINE?

06:59.553 --> 07:03.223
- UH, WE HAD LUNCH, LE CIRQUE'S,
FRIDAY 2:00-4:00.

07:03.256 --> 07:06.059
- YEAH, THAT'S A LATE LUNCH.
YOU WALK HER HOME?

07:06.093 --> 07:07.528
- I GOT HER INTO A CAB.

07:07.561 --> 07:10.998
SHE'D HAD A FEW AND...
I WENT BACK TO WORK.

07:11.031 --> 07:13.033
- HMM.

07:13.066 --> 07:14.935
- LOOK, I DON'T KNOW WHAT
CHRISTINE TOLD YOU,

07:14.968 --> 07:17.137
BUT NOTHING INAPPROPRIATE
HAPPENED ON FRIDAY.

07:17.170 --> 07:17.971
- OKAY, WHAT ABOUT LAST NIGHT?

07:18.005 --> 07:19.640
YOU MIND TELLING US
WHERE YOU WERE?

07:19.673 --> 07:22.042
- I WAS AT THE WALDORF
WITH MY WIFE.

07:22.075 --> 07:24.177
WE DON'T LIKE RESTAURANTS
ON VALENTINE'S DAY.

07:24.211 --> 07:25.278
IT'S A SUCKER PLAY.

07:25.312 --> 07:28.882
SO WE HOLE UP FOR A FEW DAYS
AND ORDER ROOM SERVICE.

07:28.916 --> 07:30.117
- THAT'S SWEET.

07:30.150 --> 07:32.853
AND HOW ABOUT YOU AND BOYD?
HOW ARE YOU GUYS GETTING ALONG?

07:32.886 --> 07:34.154
- WE'RE BEST FRIENDS

07:34.187 --> 07:35.656
SINCE PREP SCHOOL,
LIKE BROTHERS.

07:35.689 --> 07:37.525
- SO HE DIDN'T MIND
BAILING YOU OUT

07:37.558 --> 07:39.192
WHEN YOU GOT JAMMED UP
BY THE S.E.C.?

07:39.226 --> 07:42.530
- NO, IT JUST GAVE HIM SOMETHING
ELSE TO RAG ON ME ABOUT.

07:42.563 --> 07:44.164
- WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU SPOKE WITH HIM?

07:44.197 --> 07:45.933
- LAST NIGHT.

07:45.966 --> 07:47.067
HE WAS AT THE AIRPORT.

07:47.100 --> 07:48.135
HE HAD TO JUMP BECAUSE CHRISTINE

07:48.168 --> 07:49.703
WANTED TO VIDEO CHAT.

07:49.737 --> 07:53.006
WHEN SHE SAYS JUMP...

07:53.040 --> 07:55.208
- I'LL GET 'EM THE MONEY,
I'LL-I'LL...

07:55.242 --> 07:58.211
I'LL DO WHATEVER THEY WANT.
JUST TELL ME YOU'RE OKAY.

07:58.245 --> 07:59.880
- BOYD HARTWELL.
- YEAH?

07:59.913 --> 08:01.081
- WE NEED YOU TO COME WITH US.

08:01.114 --> 08:02.082
- CHRISTINE, I GOTTA GO.

08:02.115 --> 08:03.551
- BOYD, BOYD!
WAIT. WE'RE HERE TO HELP YOU.

08:03.584 --> 08:05.753
- HONEY, LISTEN, JUST TELL THEM

08:05.786 --> 08:06.754
I'LL GET THE MONEY, OKAY?

08:06.787 --> 08:07.588
NO COPS, I HEAR YOU!

08:07.621 --> 08:08.922
ALL RIGHT, I LOVE YOU,
I GOTTA GO!

08:08.956 --> 08:10.591
- STOP!
- YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND!

08:10.624 --> 08:12.159
- TAKE IT EASY, PAL.
I DON'T WANNA CUFF YOU.

08:12.192 --> 08:13.661
- I DON'T NEED YOUR HELP.

08:13.694 --> 08:15.162
LISTEN, THAT WAS MY WIFE.

08:15.195 --> 08:16.697
THEY SAID NO COPS.

08:16.730 --> 08:19.132
THEY'RE GONNA KILL HER.

08:20.668 --> 08:23.604
SHE WAS FIGHTING BACK,
BUT...

08:23.637 --> 08:26.206
HE STARTED RAPING HER.

08:26.239 --> 08:27.307
HERE.

08:27.340 --> 08:30.077
I POINTED MY CELL AT THE SCREEN.

08:30.110 --> 08:31.845
- HE WORE A MASK.

08:31.879 --> 08:36.116
MAYBE HE THOUGHT YOUR WIFE
WOULD HAVE RECOGNIZED HIM.

08:36.149 --> 08:38.185
CAN YOU THINK OF ANYONE
WITH A REASON

08:38.218 --> 08:40.053
TO HURT YOU OR YOUR WIFE?

08:40.087 --> 08:42.623
- THIS CAN'T BE
SOMEONE WHO KNOWS US.

08:42.656 --> 08:45.926
- TELL US ABOUT
THE RANSOM DEMAND.

08:45.959 --> 08:50.230
- WHEN I LANDED, THERE WAS
A VOICEMAIL FROM CHRISTINE

08:50.263 --> 08:55.335
AND SHE SAID THAT
THEY WANTED $250,000.

08:55.368 --> 08:58.171
AND SHE MADE ME PROMISE NO COPS.

08:58.205 --> 08:59.607
OKAY? I CAN HANDLE THIS
ON MY OWN.

08:59.640 --> 09:01.241
- THAT'S NOT A GOOD IDEA,
MR. HARTWELL.

09:01.274 --> 09:02.075
- NO! PLEASE.

09:02.109 --> 09:05.278
IF THEY SEE YOU,
THEY WILL KILL HER!

09:07.681 --> 09:09.583
SORRY, I HAVEN'T
SLEPT IN 20 HOURS.

09:09.617 --> 09:10.918
MY HEAD IS EXPLODING.

09:10.951 --> 09:12.686
- WE UNDERSTAND THAT.

09:12.720 --> 09:16.724
BUT YOU HAVE TO LET US HANDLE
IT, MR. HARTWELL.

09:16.757 --> 09:21.662
IT'S THE BEST CHANCE YOU HAVE
OF GETTING YOUR WIFE BACK.

09:21.695 --> 09:22.763
- LEAVE IT IN MADISON'S
BACKPACK,

09:22.796 --> 09:24.698
UNDER THE BENCH
IN THE PARK.

09:24.732 --> 09:26.333
6:00 A.M., TOMORROW.

09:26.366 --> 09:30.270
BOYD, THE SAID NO COPS OR
THEY'LL KILL ME AND MADISON.

09:30.303 --> 09:33.741
THEY KNOW EVERYTHING ABOUT US.

09:33.774 --> 09:34.775
- THEY'RE ON THE MOVE
FOR BOTH OF THE CALLS.

09:34.808 --> 09:38.045
BOUNCING OFF TOWERS
FROM 60TH TO 14TH STREET.

09:38.078 --> 09:39.212
YOU CAN HEAR TRAFFIC.

09:39.246 --> 09:40.881
- AND THEY TRACKED
HER LOCATION SINCE?

09:40.914 --> 09:43.016
- THE BATTERY WAS REMOVED AFTER
THE CALL TO THE HUSBAND.

09:43.050 --> 09:45.018
- ANY OTHER CALLS FROM HER CELL?

09:45.052 --> 09:47.821
- YEAH, TWO TO A NO-NAME PHONE.
WE'RE TRACKING THAT RIGHT NOW.

09:47.855 --> 09:51.258
- WELL, WHAT ABOUT
THE HUSBAND'S STORY?

09:51.291 --> 09:55.896
- HE SEEMS GENUINELY
TRAUMATIZED.

09:55.929 --> 09:57.297
- ALL RIGHT,
LET HIM GO HOME TO SLEEP

09:57.330 --> 10:00.367
AND TO SEE HIS DAUGHTER,
BUT I WANT A UNI ON HIM.

10:00.400 --> 10:01.769
- CAPTAIN, I DON'T THINK
HE'S IN ON THIS.

10:01.802 --> 10:03.637
- HE RAN FROM US ONCE,
HE'LL DO IT AGAIN.

10:03.671 --> 10:05.305
TARU HAVE THE TRAPS
ON HIS PHONES?

10:05.338 --> 10:07.374
- YEAH.
- NOW LET'S JUST HOPE SOMEBODY

10:07.407 --> 10:10.678
SHOWS UP AT THAT DROP
LOCATION TOMORROW.

10:14.848 --> 10:16.349
- OH, MAN.

10:16.383 --> 10:17.818
- WHAT?

10:17.851 --> 10:20.854
- VALENTINE'S DINNER;
I FORGOT.

10:23.691 --> 10:25.726
HEY.

10:25.759 --> 10:27.360
- DID YOU FORGET ABOUT DINNER?

10:27.394 --> 10:29.930
- NO, NO.

10:29.963 --> 10:31.899
UH, YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL.

10:31.932 --> 10:33.767
- THANKS.
- WE GOT JAMMED UP.

10:33.801 --> 10:35.202
- OH, I SEE,
I'M HOME FOR A WEEK,

10:35.235 --> 10:36.870
YOU'RE ALREADY
TAKING ME FOR GRANTED.

10:36.904 --> 10:37.871
- WHAT--
[chuckles]

10:37.905 --> 10:39.339
NEVER.

10:39.372 --> 10:43.376
JUST GIVE ME A MINUTE, HUH?

11:00.293 --> 11:05.298
- HEY, WATCH THAT DOG-WALKER
GOING INTO THE PARK.

11:28.355 --> 11:31.058
- FALSE ALARM.

11:38.899 --> 11:40.734
WHITE FEMALE
WEARING ALL BLACK,

11:40.768 --> 11:42.235
HEADING TOWARD THE BACKPACK.

11:43.436 --> 11:44.805
MOVE IN!

11:44.838 --> 11:46.273
- LET'S GO, LET'S GO.

11:52.545 --> 11:54.247
- POLICE! DROP IT!

11:54.281 --> 11:56.416
DROP IT!
- HELP!

11:56.449 --> 11:58.018
- HEY, TAKE IT EASY.
- NO!

11:58.051 --> 12:01.154
THEY'LL KILL ME, PLEASE!

12:01.188 --> 12:03.256
THEY'RE WATCHING!
- WHO IS?

12:03.290 --> 12:05.325
- THREE BLACK MEN!

12:05.358 --> 12:08.128
PLEASE LET ME GIVE THEM
THE MONEY! PLEASE!

12:08.161 --> 12:10.263
PLEASE!

12:10.297 --> 12:12.299
OH, GOD.
[sobbing]

12:20.307 --> 12:23.376
- THEY MADE ME
TAKE OFF MY CLOTHES...

12:23.410 --> 12:28.181
THEN THEY TOOK TURNS.

12:28.215 --> 12:32.285
SOMETIMES...TWO AT A TIME.

12:34.287 --> 12:37.324
SOMETIMES ALL THREE.

12:37.357 --> 12:40.093
MY MOUTH, EVERYWHERE.

12:40.127 --> 12:43.196
AND THEY MADE ME
