I DID WHATEVER I HAD TO DO
TO SURVIVE.

38:35.547 --> 38:36.648
- NOTHING FURTHER.

38:46.157 --> 38:48.594
- YOUR HONOR,
WE ARE UNABLE TO REACH

38:48.627 --> 38:51.062
A UNANIMOUS VERDICT
IN THIS MATTER.

38:51.096 --> 38:52.631
- I DON'T ACCEPT THAT,

38:52.664 --> 38:55.634
AND I ORDER THE JURY
TO CONTINUE TO DELIBERATE.

38:55.667 --> 38:57.035
- SIDEBAR?

38:57.068 --> 38:58.404
- APPROACH.

39:01.907 --> 39:03.875
- YOUR HONOR, I HAVE REASON
TO BELIEVE THE DEFENDANT

39:03.909 --> 39:06.011
IS INFLUENCING ONE OF
THE JURORS IN THIS CASE.

39:06.044 --> 39:07.779
- BASED ON WHAT, MS. NOVAK?

39:07.813 --> 39:09.615
- I'VE WITNESSED EYE CONTACT
ON MORE THAN ONE OCCASION

39:09.648 --> 39:11.683
BOTH INSIDE THE COURTROOM
AND OUTSIDE THE COURTROOM--

39:11.717 --> 39:12.518
- THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

39:12.551 --> 39:13.385
PROSECUTION
IS GRASPING AT STRAWS.

39:13.419 --> 39:15.587
THE WHOLE CASE IS BASED
ON THE TESTIMONY

39:15.621 --> 39:17.589
OF A CONVICTED FELON,
A DRUG DEALER,

39:17.623 --> 39:18.690
AND A CORRUPT BUSINESS PARTNER.

39:18.724 --> 39:20.726
- YOU'VE GOTTA BE KIDDING--
- ALL RIGHT, MR. EXLEY.

39:20.759 --> 39:24.396
MS. NOVAK, I WILL
QUESTION THE JUROR.

39:24.430 --> 39:26.698
- YOUR HONOR, WE MAY HAVE PASSED
EACH OTHER ONCE OR TWICE...

39:26.732 --> 39:29.501
IN THE HALLWAY OR ON THE STAIRS.

39:29.535 --> 39:34.673
- NO OUTSIDE CONTACT, NO CALLS,
TEXTS, SOCIAL MEDIA INTERACTION?

39:34.706 --> 39:37.709
- I'M A HAPPILY MARRIED MAN.

39:39.745 --> 39:41.947
- THANK YOU, YOU'RE DISMISSED.

39:43.749 --> 39:44.950
- ANY OTHER TRICKS, MS. NOVAK?

39:44.983 --> 39:46.752
- I KNOW WHAT I SAW.

39:46.785 --> 39:48.754
- UNLESS YOU HAVE EVIDENCE OF
IMPROPER COMMUNICATION,

39:48.787 --> 39:51.723
I'M NOT DISMISSING A JUROR
FOR MAKING EYE CONTACT.

39:51.757 --> 39:53.158
- [clears throat]

39:55.794 --> 39:58.129
- YOUR HONOR, I'M SORRY,

39:58.163 --> 40:00.499
WE REMAIN HOPELESSLY
DEADLOCKED.

40:02.534 --> 40:04.603
- THE CASE OF NEW YORK
AGAINST CHRISTINE HARTWELL

40:04.636 --> 40:07.839
IS HEREBY DECLARED A MISTRIAL.

40:07.873 --> 40:09.975
THE STATE OF NEW YORK THANKS YOU
FOR YOUR SERVICE.

40:10.008 --> 40:11.777
YOU'RE DISMISSED.

40:11.810 --> 40:13.545
[bangs gavel]

40:31.697 --> 40:34.199
- THIS CASE
WAS A DOG FROM THE GET.

40:34.232 --> 40:36.702
- TRY IT AGAIN.
SHE'S GUILTY.

40:36.735 --> 40:38.637
- I'LL DO MY BEST,
BUT THERE'S NOT A CHANCE

40:38.670 --> 40:41.072
THE BOSSES WILL LET
THIS GO TO RETRIAL.

40:41.106 --> 40:43.642
- HEY, EXCUSE ME, MA'AM.

40:43.675 --> 40:45.844
- YOU MIND TELLING US
WHAT WENT ON IN THERE?

40:45.877 --> 40:47.613
- 11-TO-1, GUILTY.

40:47.646 --> 40:49.548
EXCEPT FOR THIS ONE JUROR.

40:49.581 --> 40:51.016
HE SAYS HE LOOKED IN HER EYES,

40:51.049 --> 40:53.719
AND HE JUST KNEW SHE
WAS TELLING THE TRUTH.

40:53.752 --> 40:55.654
- THANK YOU.
- YOU'RE WELCOME.

40:55.687 --> 40:57.789
- I LOVE MY WIFE.

40:57.823 --> 41:00.559
AND I HAVE STOOD BY HER
AND BELIEVED HER

41:00.592 --> 41:03.061
THROUGH EVERY SECOND OF
THIS HORRIFIC NIGHTMARE.

41:03.094 --> 41:05.664
SHE HAS BEEN TO HELL AND BACK.

41:05.697 --> 41:07.966
FIRST, RAPED BY
A BRUTAL ASSAILANT

41:07.999 --> 41:10.602
AND THEN RAPED AGAIN
BY THE STATE,

41:10.636 --> 41:13.772
AND FORCED TO SUFFER THROUGH
THIS TRAVESTY OF A TRIAL.

41:13.805 --> 41:16.642
MY WIFE IS THE BRAVEST
WOMAN I KNOW.

41:16.675 --> 41:18.744
SHE IS A SURVIVOR.

41:18.777 --> 41:21.713
WE LOOK FORWARD
TO PUTTING THIS BEHIND US

41:21.747 --> 41:23.014
AND MOVING ON WITH OUR LIVES,

41:23.048 --> 41:25.283
KNOWING THAT THE STRENGTH
OF OUR LOVE

41:25.316 --> 41:27.686
HAS ONLY GROWN STRONGER
THROUGH THIS ORDEAL.

41:27.719 --> 41:33.825
[reporters calling out
questions]
